{"tid":738820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港姐複試！精選12位索女唔睇唔得","createTime":"2018-07-11T19:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T07:50:32.000Z","uid":82018,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2da4435ea3d1e8a66c29bd89cb1f4489f96ad1b5","tid":738820,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T19:06:54.000Z","msg":"港姐又嚟喇！今日嚟到複試，有51位靚女殺到入電視城，東網巨星依家為大家精選12位索女，大家唔睇絕對會後悔！ <br />\n<br />\n第一位，係「美版松岡」丁子田，佢今日着到紅噹噹，加上身材火辣辣，索呀！第二位，「出道版栢芝」Agnes，一個純字呀，但佢就相當騰雞，現身3秒就想閃！第三位，「性感超蓮」Jackie，佢同超蓮一樣靚，但就加一點野性！第四位，「港版真野惠野里菜」Amber，笑容甜美，想冧死人咩！第五位，「圓潤李若彤」梁致欣，眼大大加上圓圓哋，都幾可愛㗎！第六位，「翻版王麗嘉」Norma，同正版一樣，都係性感尤物！第七位，前As One成員陳苑澄，做過藝人嘅佢表現好淡定！第八位，「景甜胡琳混合體」Kathy，泰山裝露肩，性感又迷人！第九位，「人魚崔碧珈」Honey，擁有黝黑皮膚，夠晒陽光！第十位，「嬌小薛凱琪」楊釩，嬌滴滴好可愛呢！第十一位，「仙氣紅姑」陳曉華，佢一定唔會放屁，點解？因為靚女唔放屁㗎！最後一位，「嫩版陳爽」Rachael，高貴又大方，靚呀！ <br />\n<br />\n來源： <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180711/mobile/bkn-20180711221720776-0711_00862_001.html?eventPath=hk_entertainment&amp;eventID=402882b163f205f801646a563ab43d59\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180711%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180711221720776-0711_00862_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_entertainment%26eventID%3D402882b163f205f801646a563ab43d59&d=xCoCf8VsiGpfeKn2W5Kz0m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=88d16e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180711/mobile/bkn-20180711221720776-0711_00862_001.html?eventPath=hk_entertainment&amp;eventID=402882b163f205f801646a563ab43d59</a><br />\n東方日報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/030532_934acbc615e31ef81ad799beb34777b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F030532_934acbc615e31ef81ad799beb34777b9.png&h=2f242046&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/030533_934acbc615e31ef81ad799beb34777b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.e